---
title: 'Lokalkontor'
category: 'Kontorside'
order: 3
bodyClass: 'bg-white'
alpine: true
---

{%- extends 'base.njk' -%}

{%- macro iconBox(box) -%}
  <div class="grid isolate">
    <div class="z-10 grid w-16 mx-auto translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-100 rounded-full place-items-center aspect-square">
      {{ box.icon | svgContents('w-7 h-7 shrink-0') | safe }}
    </div>
    <div class="px-6 py-8 bg-white md:py-12 md:px-10">
      <h2 class="mt-8 text-fluid-24-28 font-semibold">{{ box.title | safe }}</h2>
      <div class="mt-2 prose markdown">
        {{ box.content | markdown | safe }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endmacro -%}


{%- block content -%}
  <main data-theme="kontor">

    <div class="grid py-16 grid-cols-combi">
      <div class="mb-8 col-main">
        <h1 class="text-fluid-32-36 font-semibold leading-tight text-gray-900 md:text-fluid-36-48">
          NAV Andeby
        </h1>
        <p class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mt-1">
          <span class="text-fluid-16-18 tracking-wider text-gray-700 uppercase">
            NAV kontor
          </span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">|</span>
          <span class="text-fluid-16-18 text-gray-600">Lokalkontor for Andeby, Gåseby og Fjærby</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-main">
        <div class="p-8 bg-orange-50">
          <h3 class="text-fluid-22-24 font-semibold">Adresse</h3>
          <address class="mt-1">
            Kvakkegata 24,<br />
            1234 Andeby
          </address>
          <p class="mt-2 text-fluid-16-18">Bruk inngang ved lekeplass</p>

          <h3 class="text-fluid-22-24 font-semibold mt-7">Åpningstider når du ikke har avtale</h3>
          <table class="mt-2 text-left">
            <tr>
              <th class="py-0.5 w-24 font-normal">Mandag</th>
              <td class="py-0.5 font-semibold">10.00–14.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="py-0.5 w-24 font-normal">Tirsdag</th>
              <td class="py-0.5 font-semibold">10.00–14.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="py-0.5 w-24 font-normal">Onsdag</th>
              <td class="py-0.5 font-semibold">10.00–14.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="py-0.5 w-24 font-normal">Torsdag</th>
              <td class="py-0.5 font-semibold">Kun timeavtale</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="py-0.5 w-24 font-normal">Fredag</th>
              <td class="py-0.5 font-semibold">10.00–14.00</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mt-7">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" >
              <path d="M12 0C5.38226 0 0 5.38226 0 12C0 18.6177 5.38226 24 12 24C18.6167 24 24 18.6177 24 12C24 5.38226 18.6167 0 12 0Z" fill="#368DA8" />
              <path d="M13.5 6.5C13.5 5.67157 12.8284 5 12 5C11.1716 5 10.5 5.67157 10.5 6.5C10.5 7.32843 11.1716 8 12 8C12.8284 8 13.5 7.32843 13.5 6.5ZM9 17V19H15V17H13V10H9V12H11V17H9Z" fill="white" />
            </svg>
            <p>Du kan avtale møte med veilederen din utenom disse åpningstidene.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 mt-7 bg-gray-50">
          <p>Telefonnummeret til NAV er <span class="block text-fluid-24-28 font-semibold leading-tight">55 55 33 33</span></p>
          <p class="pt-4">Du kan ikke ringe direkte til NAV-kontoret.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid pb-20 grid-cols-combi bg-gray-50">
      <div class="col-narrow">
        {% for box in boxes %}
          {{ iconBox(box) }}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
{%- endblock -%}

{%- block styles -%}{%- endblock -%}
{%- block script -%}{%- endblock -%}
